Package ua.kpi.comsys.test2.implementation

Class NumberListImpl

java.lang.Object
ua.kpi.comsys.test2.implementation.NumberListImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Byte>, Collection<Byte>, List<Byte>, NumberList
public class NumberListImpl extends Object implements NumberList
Custom implementation of NumberList interface. Represents a positive number where each list element stores a single digit in the current scale of notation.

Personal assignment parameters:

  • C3 = 0 - Linear doubly linked (bidirectional) list
  • C5 = 2 - Octal number system
  • Additional scale: Decimal number system
  • C7 = 5 - Algebraic and logical AND of two numbers
